{"tid":1858982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣俾啲鬼佬辨認我係香港人好","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T06:02:21.000Z","uid":152339,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe16885fd3fd3e930e15e2753f395d6a853fcc2","tid":1858982,"uid":152339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"話說今朝睇咗呢個post<br />\n<br />\n中國人因戴口罩被英國人攻擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857801</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁我嚟緊就會去外國旅行，如果仲未封香港嘅話。<br />\n我諗左好撚耐，點樣俾啲鬼佬知道我係香港人。<br />\n本身諗住買件I&rsquo;m Hong Konger過去著，<br />\n點知原來2014之後已經冇晒貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家得翻啲五大訴求Tee。<br />\n屌你咩鬼佬一定睇得明中文字啦！<br />\n不過諗諗吓，如果着住件我係香港人，<br />\n一陣唔係比鬼佬打，係比支那人追住打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但屌你我唔夠秋都算，一陣野埋沙士就仆街。<br />\n於是我諗左一個嘅方案。<br />\n<br />\n我着件為所欲為I ❤️ HK Tee去咪得囉！<br />\n又唔會俾支那人打，所以為所欲為Tee就最fit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n橫掂鬼佬都淨係睇字，唔知件衫嘅背後意義<br />\n係支那人眼中就係止暴制亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />safe<br />\n<br />\n所以請問邊度可以買到為所欲為Tee<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca64ab259b24822dd4a3d1bc1fc0f94ce6ec78f","tid":1858982,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"紋身"},{"pid":"45d88e12e59b856d8fda4ebb850eca83da538ccb","tid":1858982,"uid":152339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ca64ab259b24822dd4a3d1bc1fc0f94ce6ec78f","tid":1858982,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"紋身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"紋乜野先"},{"pid":"c37ac451c88cf14cc308585ddf8c2e45deb00168","tid":1858982,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"鬼佬都好醒<br />\n知道支持港獨先係真香港人"},{"pid":"e00a10081